{
  "texts": [
    "We aspire for this article, with its in-depth overview and discussions, to furnish academia with innovative research ideas while simultaneously offering industry practitioners and adopters valuable references for best practices.",
    "In other words, we hope this document can be a useful educational tool, inspiring both the current workforce and the next generation to engage in research and development in the field of privacy.",
    "In the following, we provide a brief overview of the topics covered in this article.",
    "There are many high-profile deployments of DP in industries and in the public sector.",
    "However, there are several common challenges that arise during these deployments."
  ]
}